.name
Drip
.author
Art Skiles 
.description
Drip is an arcade style game with 15 floors (levels).  You must move along
the pipes of each floor and rust them to advance to the next level. Every 3
floors completed will entitle you to a bonus round where extra drips can be
won.  An extra drip will also be awarded for every 10,000 points.  
